title: Paina Lanai Food Court
seo_title: Paina Lanai Food Court | Attractions in Waikiki
seo_description: Situated in the Royal Hawaiian Center is Paina Lanai Food Court with lots of options, perfect for a bite to eat during your trip to Waikiki.
address: (Royal Hawaiian Center) 2201 Kalakaua Ave, Bldg B, 2nd-floor Honolulu
contents_1: From local favorites to well-known chains, there are plenty of options in this large food court inside the Royal Hawaiian Center.
description: Located in the Royal Hawaiian Center, the Paina Lanai Food Court has plenty of options. Try a steak at Champion’s Steak & Seafood, smoked Hayashi curry at Curry Caféramen at Ezogiku, or a burger at the local burger shop Mahaloha Burgers. There are also other favorites like Maui Tacos, Subway, and Sbarro.
